Tastefully upgraded 3-bed townhouse for rent in Inspirada in Anthem. 1,800+ Sqft with 3 bedrooms+Loft, 2.5 bathrooms and a 2-car garage that opens up to a back alley. Cozy front porch entrance. Open great room with plush carpeting, neutral colors, and upgraded fixtures. Fabulous chefs kitchen with island/breakfast bar, pantry, upgraded cabinets, granite countertops, and all appliances. All 3 bedrooms+bonus loft upstairs. Half bath downstairs. Carpeting in bedrooms and tile floors in bathrooms. Large primary bedroom with walk-in closet. Dual sinks with large shower in main bathroom. Laundry room with full size washer and dryer. Guest bedrooms share a full bath upstairs. <br>
***Amenities include community pools with spa, Clubhouse with gym and lounge, basketball court, tennis courts, children's playground, dog park, walk/bike trails and skate park. <br>
